text: Hyparpax is a genus of moths of the family Notodontidae described by Jacob Hübner in 1825. ==Species== *Hyparpax aurora (Smith, 1797) *Hyparpax venus Neumoegen, 1892 *Hyparpax minor (Barnes & Benjamin, 1924) *Hyparpax aurostriata Graef, 1888 *Hyparpax perophoroides (Strecker, 1876) ==External links== * Category:Notodontidae
title: Hyparpax
